    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Extinct order of fossil marine reptiles having a stout, sometimes armoured body and large flat palatal teeth, thought to have been used for crushing mollusc shells dating to the Triassic.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
